---
layout: landing.njk
title: Cartographer (private build) | Ionrift Workshop
description: Private build of Cartographer for dogfooding.
canonical: https://ionrift.cloud/cartographer/app/
noindex: true
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
draft: true
bodyClass: page-cartographer
---

{% include "landing/nav.njk" %}

<main class="page-main module-detail page-cartographer">
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="page-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
            <span>{{ cartographer.name }}</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
            <span>Private build</span>
        </nav>

        <header class="module-detail-header" style="--module-color: {{ cartographer.accent }}; --module-icon-color: {{ cartographer.iconAccent or cartographer.accent }};">
            <div class="module-detail-icon">
                <img src="{{ cartographer.icon }}" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="module-detail-intro">
                <span class="module-pill pill-ea">Private build</span>
                <h1 class="module-detail-title">{{ cartographer.name }}</h1>
                <p class="module-detail-tag" style="color: {{ cartographer.accent }};">{{ cartographer.tagline }}</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="module-detail-body ionrift-window">
            <p class="module-detail-desc">An unlisted entry point for testing the hosted app before early access. Sign-in is gated to Patreon, Acolyte tier and above.</p>

            <div class="module-detail-copy">
                <p>Generation runs against a monthly credit allowance. Failed generations are not charged. Finished maps are kept for 30 days, then removed, so download anything worth keeping.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="module-detail-disclosure">
                <p>{{ cartographer.disclosure }}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="module-detail-actions">
{% if cartographer.dogfoodAppUrl %}
                <a href="{{ cartographer.dogfoodAppUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary module-detail-cta">Launch Cartographer</a>
{% else %}
                <span class="btn btn-ghost module-detail-cta module-detail-cta--disabled">Not configured</span>
{% endif %}
            </div>

            <p class="module-install-note">Unlisted on purpose. This page is not linked from the site and is excluded from search.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="page-back">
            <a href="/">&larr; Home</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</main>

{% include "landing/footer.njk" %}
